article.headline: Gaiter scores 20, guides South Alabama past Spring Hill 91-74
article.description: — Isiah Gaiter's 20 points helped South Alabama defeat Spring Hill 91-74 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Gaiter scores 20, guides South Alabama past Spring Hill 91-74
article.story: MOBILE, Ala. -- — Isiah Gaiter's 20 points helped South Alabama defeat Spring Hill 91-74 on Saturday night. Gaiter also contributed six assists and three steals for the Jaguars (6-5). Samuel Tabe added 19 points while going 7 of 13 and 5 of 5 from the free throw line, and they also had eight rebounds. Marcus Millender had 12 points and was 4 of 9 shooting, including 1 for 4 from 3-point range, and went 3 for 4 from the line. Walter Peggs Jr. finished with 17 points for the Badgers. Isaiah Veal added 14 points for Spring Hill. In addition, Timothy Reilly had 13 points, 10 rebounds and two blocks. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
